程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.examples.power.planetlab

类 PlanetLabRunner

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.examples.power.RunnerAbstract
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.examples.power.planetlab.PlanetLabRunner
public class PlanetLabRunner
extends RunnerAbstract
The example runner for the PlanetLab workload. If you are using any algorithms, policies or workload included in the power package please cite the following paper: Anton Beloglazov, and Rajkumar Buyya, "Optimal Online Deterministic Algorithms and Adaptive Heuristics for Energy and Performance Efficient Dynamic Consolidation of Virtual Machines in Cloud Data Centers", Concurrency and Computation: Practice and Experience (CCPE), Volume 24, Issue 13, Pages: 1397-1420, John Wiley & Sons, Ltd, New York, USA, 2012
从以下版本开始:
Jan 5, 2012
